{
  "stem": "9.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And if you realize what that is, it's a tablecloth that has shiny and dull designs on it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I had to make a-- cover up a hole that looked exactly like part of the fabric.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was quite an art.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But at that time, every so-called lady of the house had to learn how to do it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was not allowed to ride a bicycle, because it isn't very nice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It isn't proper for a lady to ride a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was supposed to write, play piano, learn literature, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In my childhood, I was a very skinny child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Vitamins were not available, so in order to get the iron into my system, a juice from vegetables, from beets and carrots and turnips, and various healthy things, was made, and I had to drink an eight-ounce glass every single day.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I also had to eat raw ground liver with onions with some seasoning in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But in order to bribe me to eat it, I was getting $1 a glass or a $1 a little liver.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And that was a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Well, it wasn't really $1.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was zloty, which was Polish money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "After I saved all the money, I bought my own piano.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So that was how they accomplished getting some vitamins into my system.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The household was very, very well kept.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We had a routine every single day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was always catered to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I could do anything I pleased.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "What makes it so interesting when you hear it later is when I'm suddenly left alone, I'm able to cope after being so spoiled.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And that's still a very big mystery to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
